server <- function(input, output) {
  output$map <- renderLeaflet({
    leaflet(data = data) %>%
      addTiles() %>%
      addCircleMarkers(
        lat = ~Latitude,
        lng = ~Longitude,
        radius = sqrt(data$MedianResalePrice) / 100,  # Adjust the radius based on the price
        fillOpacity = 0.7,
        color = "RGB(127,0,255)",
        stroke = FALSE,
        label = ~paste("Town: ", Town, "<br>Median Resale Price: $", MedianResalePrice)
      ) %>%
      addProviderTiles("Stamen.Watercolor")  # You can choose different map styles
  })
}
